platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: For diehard music fans, nothing’s worse than finding out your favorite band came through town and you missed a killer show. Songkick cleverly connects you with concerts you’re likely to be interested in and notifies you of upcoming gigs by artists you listen to. We love using the slick interface to browse hotly anticipated shows at home and around the world (road trip, anyone?), and being able to buy tickets within the app totally rocks.
